TITLE VirtaSysIdentityInterface2026v1
VERSION 1
CATEGORY GOV

SUMMARY
Non-actuating identity and shard metadata interface for Virta-Sys.

fields
  requestid         string
  operation         string   # e.g. ResolveRepo, ResolveIdentity, ListShards
  githubslug        string   # optional
  legacy_login      string   # optional
  current_login     string   # optional
  bostrom_address   string   # optional
  shardid           int32    # optional
  response_json     string   # JSON-encoded summary of resolved entities
  issued_utc        string
  proofrefhex       string
